### Admin login (seed: admin@graphify.dev / admin1234)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@graphify.dev",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### GET prompts — 성공
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/prompts?type=RELATION_ANALYSIS
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### GET prompts — 실패 (type 오류)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/prompts?type=INVALID
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### POST save — 성공
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "RELATION_ANALYSIS",
  "systemPrompt": "당신은 기업 관계 분석 전문 AI입니다.",
  "taskTemplate": "관계 그래프 관점에서 핵심 연결을 요약하세요.",
  "changeNote": "API 테스트 저장"
}

### POST test — 성공 (companyId=1 가정)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/prompts/1/test
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyId": 1,
  "sampleInput": "반도체 공급망 중심으로 분석"
}

### POST rollback — 성공 (targetVersionId는 GET 응답 versions[1].id 사용)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/v1/admin/prompts/1/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetVersionId": 1
}
